  <source>Children's Research Institute</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate a touch screen application designed to help
      pediatric patients with cerebral palsy communicate. The study will test how well patients
      type on two different tools: one tool is already on the market , and the second tool is a
      newly developed App.
    </textblock>
